column2: SELECT top #  ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY z ASC) AS Row,   (ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY z ASC) % #) + # AS Batch,   bestObjId, z, so.survey, subclass, ra, dec, platequality, isbest,  &&& + survey + &&& +  cast(run2d as varchar(#)) + &&& + format(plate, &&&) +  &&& + format(plate, &&&) + &&& + cast(mjd as varchar(#)) +   &&& + format(fiberid, &&&) + &&& as url FROM specObj so join platex p on so.plateid = p.plateid WHERE class = &&& and zWarning = # AND bestObjId > #   AND survey IN (&&&, &&&)  AND snMedian > #  AND (z > # AND z < #)  AND (so.htmid*# & #) < (# * #)  and scienceprimary=# ORDER BY z
